description:
Season: 19
Original Air Date: 8/02/2006

Donna, Brooke, Nick and Bridget look over a few of Donna’s modeling photos. Brooke tells Donna that she is off to a great start. Brooke begins to feel envious of Donna being in the spotlight. Though Stephanie is not happy with Donna replacing Brooke, she is impressed by Donna’s photos.  Brooke arrives for Donna’s photo shoot and feels that Ridge’s vision for Donna’s photos is too provocative.  Everyone at the photo shoot is surprised by Brooke’s reaction. Later, Ridge tries to comfort Donna and Donna kisses Ridge.  Brooke walks in on the kiss and is furious. Taylor feels guilty about killing Darla and not telling Thorne.  Thorne approaches Taylor and senses that she is keeping a secret. Thorne supports Taylor and takes her to an AA meeting.
